<p>I, uh, think you missed my point. I write plans and create documents for a living. If I was annoyed with a coworker I would not create a Behavior Plan about it. The format in nonsensical and is working at cross purposes with the actual (very good) story. It's format-screw for the sake of format-screw. Show me a HR complaint report, not a SCP.</p>

